task.p:
Set y = t and then compute the parametric equation for x. Set \uvec{x} to be the variable vector \uvec{x} = \left[\begin{smallmatrix}x\\y\end{smallmatrix}\right]. Fill in the vectors at below. Then compare with .

		\uvec{x}
		\;\;=\;\;\begin{bmatrix}x\\y\end{bmatrix}
		\;\;=\;\;\begin{bmatrix}\hphantom{3+2t}\\t\end{bmatrix}
		\;\;=\;\;\begin{bmatrix}\hphantom{3}\\\hphantom{0}\end{bmatrix}
		\;\;+\;\; t\begin{bmatrix}\hphantom{2}\\\hphantom{1}\end{bmatrix}
